additionalProperty.name: Contains
additionalProperty.value: 2,4 Dimethyl-3-Cyclohexen-1-Carboxaldehyde, Dl-Limonene(Racemic), Citral, Alpha-iso-Methylionone, Methyl Cinnamate, Delta-1(2,6,6-Trimethyl-3-Cyclohexen-1-yl)-2 Buten-1-One, Linaloon.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Use only as directed. Read & retain instructions. Use in well ventilated areas. May produce an allergic reaction. Keep out of reach of children and pets. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label at hand. If in eyes: Rinse cautiously with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses if present and easy to do-continue rinsing. If on skin: Wash with soap and water. If skin irritation or a rash occurs: Get medical advice/attention. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 131 126; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor.
